.\u003C\/li\u003E\r\n\t\u003Cli\u003EHealth System retirees should be aware that they will not be able to retain their UVA email addresses, but can contact Accounts to retain Netbadge and Eservices access.\u003C\/li\u003E\r\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Ch2\u003EInterlibrary Loan (ILL)\u003C\/h2\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Cp\u003ERetired faculty can continue to request books through ILL. These will be delivered to their department or individual office if applicable.\u003C\/p\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Ch2\u003EEvents\u003C\/h2\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Cp\u003EAll UVA retirees are welcome at Library events that are open to the public. This includes lectures, classes, exhibit openings, and the like. Please come!\u003C\/p\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Ch2\u003EComputer use\u003C\/h2\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EPublic computers are available within most UVA libraries\u003C\/strong\u003E.\u003C\/p\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Cul\u003E\r\n\t\u003Cli\u003EA picture ID is required to log on, and access may be limited at certain times of the semester, as\u0026nbsp;\u003Cstrong\u003EUVA students, faculty, and staff have to be our top priority\u003C\/strong\u003E.\u003C\/li\u003E\r\n\t\u003Cli\u003EIf you have a laptop, you can get a wireless PIN by presenting a picture ID at Alderman, Brown, and Clemons.\u003C\/li\u003E\r\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\r\n","format":"basic_html","summary":""}],"field_parent_page":[{"target_id":1107,"target_type":"node","target_uuid":"8d40f2c4-6a70-4e17-b1c2-7984b32909ac","url":"\/node\/1107"}],"field_path":[{"value":"\/services\/retirees"}],"field_serve_via_iframe":[],"field_sidebar":[],"field_subnav":[],"field_upload_a_file":[]},{"nid":[{"value":907}],"uuid":[{"value":"e73d18bd-85f3-4460-ab4d-0bf38d366690"}],"vid":[{"value":3339}],"langcode":[{"value":"en"}],"type":[{"target_id":"page","target_type":"node_type","target_uuid":"17745858-15d2-4bcb-bc99-14fe05bb598b"}],"status":[{"value":true}],"title":[{"value":"Library Home Page"}],"uid":[{"target_id":4,"target_type":"user","target_uuid