d archives, as well as digital image collections, maps, musical scores, DVDs and more.\u003C\/p\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Cp\u003EThe Library regularly receives major grant funding, especially for its digital and preservation projects. Its special collections are internationally known, particularly in the area of American history, literature, and culture. The Library builds collaborative programs with scholars from around the University and other institutions, creating a vibrant environment of collegial innovation.\u003C\/p\u003E\r\n\u003Ca href=\u0022\/facts\/\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022\u0022 data-caption=\u0022UVA Library Facts\u0022 data-entity-type=\u0022file\u0022 data-entity-uuid=\u0022e6f3419f-02ba-4714-b963-2b5f022acd05\u0022 height=\u0022260\u0022 src=\u0022\/sites\/default\/files\/inline-images\/tj-rotunda_0.png\u0022 width=\u0022257\u0022 \/\u003E\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022\/press\/annual-reports\/\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022\u0022 data-caption=\u0022Annual Reports\u0022 data-entity-type=\u0022file\u0022 data-entity-uuid=\u0022f66a9712-1a54-42b5-93b1-307675dedd6d\u0022 height=\u0022254\u0022 src=\u0022\/sites\/default\/files\/inline-images\/AR2014_coverTN_0.png\u0022 width=\u0022254\u0022 \/\u003E\u003C\/a\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http:\/\/static.lib.virginia.edu\/directory\/staff\/jmu2m.html\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022John Unsworth\u0022 data-caption=\u0022University Librarian\u0022 data-entity-type=\u0022file\u0022 data-entity-uuid=\u0022abbfd963-4de9-48a8-9f1a-495b3a3d14e7\u0022 height=\u0022250\u0022 src=\u0022\/sites\/default\/files\/inline-images\/JohnUnsworth_TNforPress_0.png\u0022 width=\u0022250\u0022 \/\u003E\u003C\/a\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Ch2\u003EContact Information\u003C\/h2\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EFor images, interview contacts, and other information,\u003C\/strong\u003E please contact:\u003C\/p\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022mailto:jph9e@virginia.edu\u0022\u003EJeff Hill\u003C\/a\u003E, Communication