eprompter\u003C\/li\u003E\r\n\t\u003Cli\u003Epanel-controlled lighting\u003C\/li\u003E\r\n\t\u003Cli\u003Elive PA system\u003C\/li\u003E\r\n\t\u003Cli\u003Emultiple audio inputs with wired lavalier microphones\u003C\/li\u003E\r\n\t\u003Cli\u003Einterchangeable backdrop system\u003C\/li\u003E\r\n\t\u003Cli\u003Ea consultant in the studio to facilitate production\u003C\/li\u003E\r\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Ch3\u003EStaffing\u003C\/h3\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Cp\u003EThe RMC staff provide full-time and student consultants to teach and assist with projects.\u003C\/p\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Ch3\u003EHours of Operation\u003C\/h3\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Cp\u003EThe studio follows the RMC schedule and closes 15 minutes before the Center.\u003C\/p\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Ch3\u003EThree steps to getting started\u003C\/h3\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Cp\u003EStep 1: Fill out the information form at the following URL:\u003C\/p\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https:\/\/docs.google.com\/spreadsheet\/embeddedform?formkey=dDJ1ZlBFYWRWME9yWTM4cC1kZm1vU2c6MQ\u0022\u003EStudio 301 Application Form\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Cp\u003EStep 2: Coordinate a project review session with an \u003Ca href=\u0022mailto:teachlearn@virginia.edu\u0022\u003ERMC\u003C\/a\u003E staff member.\u003C\/p\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Cp\u003EStep 3: Once approved, coordinate reservations through the our \u003Ca href=\u0022http:\/\/cal.lib.virginia.edu\/booking\/videostudio\u0022\u003Eonline reservation system\u003C\/a\u003E.\u003C\/p\u003E\r\n","format":"basic_html","summary":""}],"field_parent_page":[{"target_id":761,"target_type":"node","target_uuid":"5a21cf33-15a4-4097-a984-5d979cd1577f","url":"\/node\/761"}],"field_path":[{"value":"\/services\/media-screening-classrooms\/studio-301\/"}],"field_serve_via_iframe":[],"field_sidebar":[],"field_subnav":[],"field_upload_a_file":[]},{"nid":[{"value":762}],"uuid":[{"value":"1e79f38f-beda-4ca2-b871-b9f50315836c"}],"vid":[{"value":2238}],"langcode":[{"value":"en"}],"type":[{"t