ong\u003Econnect your laptop to the University\u2019s wired network with an ethernet card\u003C\/strong\u003E.\r\n\t\u003Cul\u003E\r\n\t\t\u003Cli\u003EAsk the library staff about the location of network ports. Network cables are available for checkout at\u0026nbsp;\u003Ca href=\u0022\/libraries\/#alderman\u0022\u003EAlderman\u003C\/a\u003E,\u0026nbsp;\u003Ca href=\u0022\/libraries\/#clemons\u0022\u003EClemons\u003C\/a\u003E, and the\u0026nbsp;\u003Ca href=\u0022\/services\/computing\/libraries\/#science\u0022\u003ECharles L. Brown Science \u0026amp; Engineering\u003C\/a\u003E\u0026nbsp;libraries.\u003C\/li\u003E\r\n\t\u003C\/ul\u003E\r\n\t\u003C\/li\u003E\r\n\t\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EA note to UVA Retirees:\u0026nbsp;\u003C\/strong\u003ESome Library access privileges can remain after retirement.\u0026nbsp;\u003Ca href=\u0022\/services\/computing\/\u0022\u003EFind out more.\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\r\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Ch3\u003EGuests\u003C\/h3\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Cul\u003E\r\n\t\u003Cli\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EGuests of the University can\u0026nbsp;obtain a temporary passcode\u003C\/strong\u003E\u0026nbsp;to connect to U.Va.\u2019s unencrypted wireless network.\r\n\r\n\t\u003Cul\u003E\r\n\t\t\u003Cli\u003EThis passcode can be obtained from the service desks in\u0026nbsp;\u003Ca href=\u0022\/libraries\/#alderman\u0022\u003EAlderman\u003C\/a\u003E,\u0026nbsp;\u003Ca href=\u0022\/libraries\/#clemons\u0022\u003EClemons\u003C\/a\u003E, and\u0026nbsp;\u003Ca href=\u0022\/libraries\/#science\u0022\u003EBrown Science \u0026amp; Engineering\u003C\/a\u003E\u0026nbsp;libraries.\u003C\/li\u003E\r\n\t\t\u003Cli\u003EYou will need to show a\u0026nbsp;\u003Cstrong\u003Ephoto ID\u003C\/strong\u003E\u0026nbsp;and provide your\u0026nbsp;\u003Cstrong\u003Ename\u003C\/strong\u003E\u0026nbsp;and\u0026nbsp;\u003Cstrong\u003Ee-mail address\u003C\/strong\u003E\u0026nbsp;at the time the passcode is issued.\u003C\/li\u003E\r\n\t\t\u003Cli\u003EThe passcode is\u0026nbsp;\u003Cstrong\u003Evalid for 28\u0026nbsp;days\u003C\/strong\u003E; when it expires, you will need to request a new one.\u003C\/li\u003E\r\n\t\u003C\/ul\u003E\r\n\t\u003C\/li\u003E\r\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Ch2\u003EProblems Using Your Laptop or Computing Device in the Library\u003C\/h2\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Cp\u003EPlease call\u0026nbsp;the\u0026nbsp;\u003Ca href=\u0022http:\/\/its.virginia.edu\/helpdesk\/\u0022\u003EITS Help Desk\u003C\/a\u003E\u0026nbsp;at 434-924-4357 for technical assistance.\u003C\/p\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Cp\u003E\u0026nbsp;\u003C\/p\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Cp\u003ELearn more about\u0026nbsp;\u003Ca href=\u0022\/services\/digitization\/\u0022\u003EDigitization\u003C\/a\u003E\u0026nbsp;|\u0026nbsp;\u003Ca href=\u0022\/services\/printing-photocopying\/\u0022\u003EPrinting \u0026amp; Photocopying\u003C\/a\u003E\u0026nbsp;|\u0026nbsp;\u003Ca href=\u0022\/services\/scanning-self-service\/\u0022\u003ESelf-Service Scanning\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Cp\u003E\u0026nbsp;\u003C\/p\u003E\r\n","format":"basic_html","summary":""}],"field_parent_page":[{"target_id":1107,"target_type":"node","target_uuid":"8d40f2c4-6a70-4e17-b1c2-7984b32909ac","url":"\/node\/1107"}],"field_path":[{"value":"\/services\/computing"}],"field_serve_via_iframe":[],"field_sidebar":[],"field_subnav":[],"field_upload_a_file":[]},{"nid":[{"value":750}],"uuid":[{"value":"29f6de6c-09d4-4ed1-8bd2-3254a81e1859"}],"vid":[{"value":3824}],"langcode":[{"value":"en"}],"type":[{"target_id":"page","target_type":"node_type","target_uuid":"17745858-15d2-4bcb-bc99-14fe05bb598b"}],"status":[{"value":true}],"title":[{"value":"Community Patrons"}],"uid":[{"target_id":22,"target_type":"user","target_uuid":"0da2c5ee-4a8f-40a4-9b16-d3a48431aed1","url":"\/user\/22"}],"created":[{"value":1498238177}],"changed":[{"value":1521215743}],"promote":[{"value":false}],"sticky":[{"value":false}],"revision_timestamp":[{"value":1521215743}],"revision_uid":[{"target_id":12,"target_type":"user","target_uuid":"43