ices account:\u003C\/p\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Cul\u003E\r\n\t\u003Cli\u003EVisit the \u003Ca href=\u0022\/services\/ils\/\u0022\u003EILS web page\u003C\/a\u003E\u003C\/li\u003E\r\n\t\u003Cli\u003EClick on the First Time Users link at the bottom of the ILS Request Sign In logon form\u003C\/li\u003E\r\n\t\u003Cli\u003EOn the New User Registration page choose\u0026nbsp;\u0027Distance Education Student\/SCPS\u0027 as your status type\u003C\/li\u003E\r\n\u003C\/ul\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EIf you live outside the Charlottesville \/Albemarle County area\u003C\/strong\u003E, please read instructions at the bottom of the ILS registration form under \u003Cem\u003EUsers who live outside Charlottesville \/Albemarle County area\u003C\/em\u003E. Also, please be sure to list a \u201csecure\u201d address, where packages of books may be left if you\u2019re not home.\u003C\/p\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EIf you live inside the Charlottesville \/Albemarle County area\u003C\/strong\u003E, you will need an Interlibrary Services (ILS) account to request books from other libraries, or to request books listed in VIRGO with an Ivy Annex or Ivy Stacks locations. However, you are not eligible for our delivery service and will need to pick your books up from a U.Va. Library.\u003C\/p\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Ch2\u003EDelivery Address\u003C\/h2\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Cp\u003EPlease ensure that your \u003Cstrong\u003Eaddress in the ILS system is current and correct.\u0026nbsp;Your ILS account is separate from your regular Library account, and your address must be updated manually.\u003C\/strong\u003E If items are sent to an old or incorrect address, you are still responsible for these items. \u003Cstrong\u003EIf they are irretrievable, then you will be billed for them.\u003C\/strong\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Ch2\u003EDelivery of Material\u003C\/h2\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Cp\u003EArticles will be delivered via e-mail in PDF format.\u003C\/p\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Cp\u003EBooks will be delivered to you via US Mail.\u003C\/p\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Ch2\u003EReturn Process\u003C\/h2\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Cp\u003EWe will be \u003Cstrong\u003Eincluding a return mailing label in each package\u003C\/strong\u003E of materials we mail to you. \u0026nbsp;The label will be attached to the ILS paperwork enclosed. \u0026nbsp;When you are ready to return the items, simply place the label on the package and return via the U.S. Postal Service. \u0026nbsp;(Remember, you must return all materials in a secure box.) \u0026nbsp;Plan to return your items 2-3 days before the due date to ensure they are returned on time.\u003C\/p\u003E\r\n\r\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cem\u003E*Please note that materials may \u003Cstrong\u003Enot\u003C\/strong\u003E be returned to another institution for mailing.\u003C\/em\u003E\u003C\/p\u003E\r\n","format":"basic_html","summary":""}],"field_parent_page":[{"target_id":740,"target_type":"node","target_uuid":"0621b7c9-ddb1-4279-bd07-aa8f362fea33","url":"\/node\/740"}],"field_path":[{"value":"\/services\/ils\/scps-distance-education-delivery\/"}],"field_serve_via_iframe":[{"value":false}],"field_sidebar":[{"target_id":24,"target_type":"block_content","target_uuid":"9393320d-b6ce-4577-a7d2-e29bb99271c0","url":"\/block\/24"}],"field_subnav":[{"target_id":23,"target_type":"block_content","target_uuid":"9ddddbce-5c5c-4bbc-b4f3-8569a9593469","url":"\/block\/23"}],"field_upload_a_file":[]},{"nid":[{"value":744}],"uuid":[{"value":"be09f450-6355-44b2-bad9-097a5b7f81d7"}],"vid":[{"value":3930}],"langcode":[{"value":"en"}],"type":[{"target_id":"page","target_type":"node_type","target_uuid":"17745858-15d2-4bcb-bc99-14fe05bb598b"}],"status":[{"value":true}],"title":[{"value":"Lending to other libraries"}],"uid":[{"target_id":26,"target_type":"user","target_uuid":"507db1cb-861f-490d-a7fe-370e14b1c1e8","url":"\/user\/26"}],"created":[{"value":1498233850}],"changed":[{"value":1521580476}],"promote":[{"value":false}],"sticky":[{"value":false}],"revision_timestamp":[{"val